collectionMetadata.name: Monthly Statistics on Off Peak Cars (Including Population of OPC/WEC)
collectionMetadata.description:
Off peak cars (OPC) include Weekend cars (WEC) and Revised OPCs(ROPC).

More information on OPC and ROPC schemes can be found at LTA.gov.sg under Roads and Motoring ([link](https://www.lta.gov.sg/content/ltaweb/en/roads-and-motoring/transport-options-for-motorists/revised-off-peak-car-and-opc-and-weekend-car.html))
